{"tid":1818520,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"修例風波：41名公務員被捕  31人已停職","createTime":"2020-01-10T03:32:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-10T03:45:15.000Z","uid":153956,"like":2,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"8287bbb2fa5558585afcbd3e178370abba9b9bfc","tid":1818520,"uid":153956,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T03:32:42.000Z","msg":"熱烈地彈琴~~~<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n公務員事務局局長羅智光今(10日)表示，截至去年12月31日，有41名公務員因牽涉非法公眾活動而被捕，當中31人已被停職，餘下個案則積極跟進當中。他強調政府對公務員違法是零容忍，不會姑息縱容。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200110/bkn-20200110110919768-0110_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20200110%2Fbkn-20200110110919768-0110_00822_001.html&d=eKFc4b3FQa1ReKUUeYtKdKCH8iT5eEApQhURqQe1KTk%3D&h=0eac7ef8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200110/bkn-20200110110919768-0110_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"e2896a6a8796eb0804f91a1d7527a924c7a082c7","tid":1818520,"uid":198590,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T03:32:47.000Z","msg":"會員 <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">#153956 - 千萬窮能</span></strong> 極有可能係<span style=\"color: gold;\">五毛, 分化撚, mon-post狗或網軍</span><br />\n請大家保持批判性思考，善用不推文回覆，該會員以往言論：<br />\n<br />\n<code>係時候諗定輸左後點做 - #1</code><br />\n<blockquote>唔係講笑各位連青人, 係時候諗定, 日日9叫唱歌既革命輸得7788, 準備比人上門清算<br />\n<br />\n1,2,3,4定10年, 寫定張平安紙交帶</blockquote><a href=\"http://lihkg.com/thread/1687659/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lihkg.com/thread/1687659/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<code>睇你地班人既所謂革命 - #1</code><br />\n<blockquote>黎黎去去係街9 叫<br />\n<br />\n見警就縮<br />\n<br />\n咁攪法攪到幾時先成功？留比你地個孫接手曱命？<br />\n<br />\n初初都好笑消閒下時間，可惜越睇越悶<